Welcome to Geothermal Chattanooga

If you like the idea of recycling your paper and other stuff at home…Or the savings of driving a fuel-efficient car appeals to you, then Geothermal is the logical next step.

It’s sustainable, green and saves you money every month on energy bills.

With a slight premium over conventional HVAC systems, Geothermal systems help pay for themselves in energy savings and last nearly twice as long. Factor in the 30% Federal Tax Credit and a WaterFurnace Geothermal system, installed by Engineered Services Co-operative, can pay for itself in as little as 5 years.

Click on our HOW GEOTHERMAL WORKS video above to see how it works.
